  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On a remote island lost in the ocean, an ancient castle rises — the last sanctuary of magic, sealed within runic stones that sustain the very essence of the world. But darkness is relentlessly advancing. Armies of resurrected undead, led by a malevolent overlord determined to extinguish the final remnants of light, crash wave after wave against the walls of this sacred place.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/4fe92f0db0a7816f5f1d13bb3970e254.poster.avif?t=1747330010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/4fe92f0db0a7816f5f1d13bb3970e254.webm?t=1747330010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/4fe92f0db0a7816f5f1d13bb3970e254.mp4?t=1747330010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > You will experience:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dynamic gameplay and epic battles against the undead army.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrading physical and magical abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhancing armor and weapons to crush enemies more effectively.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting items and elixirs to aid in combat.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizing character armor and weapons using souls collected in battle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/7469d3c410a7b59c848c1c66d2ea0ba0.poster.avif?t=1747330010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/7469d3c410a7b59c848c1c66d2ea0ba0.webm?t=1747330010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/7469d3c410a7b59c848c1c66d2ea0ba0.mp4?t=1747330010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you preserve the spark of light by defending the runic stones from total destruction? Or will this world sink forever into the abyss of oblivion?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/a81d9ceb854fea2187bc4d75157fa2dd.poster.avif?t=1747330010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/a81d9ceb854fea2187bc4d75157fa2dd.webm?t=1747330010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/a81d9ceb854fea2187bc4d75157fa2dd.mp4?t=1747330010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On a remote island lost in the ocean, an ancient castle rises — the last sanctuary of magic, sealed within runic stones that sustain the very essence of the world. But darkness is relentlessly advancing. Armies of resurrected undead, led by a malevolent overlord determined to extinguish the final remnants of light, crash wave after wave against the walls of this sacred place.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/4fe92f0db0a7816f5f1d13bb3970e254.poster.avif?t=1747330010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/4fe92f0db0a7816f5f1d13bb3970e254.webm?t=1747330010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/4fe92f0db0a7816f5f1d13bb3970e254.mp4?t=1747330010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > You will experience:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dynamic gameplay and epic battles against the undead army.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrading physical and magical abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhancing armor and weapons to crush enemies more effectively.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting items and elixirs to aid in combat.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizing character armor and weapons using souls collected in battle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/7469d3c410a7b59c848c1c66d2ea0ba0.poster.avif?t=1747330010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/7469d3c410a7b59c848c1c66d2ea0ba0.webm?t=1747330010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/7469d3c410a7b59c848c1c66d2ea0ba0.mp4?t=1747330010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you preserve the spark of light by defending the runic stones from total destruction? Or will this world sink forever into the abyss of oblivion?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/a81d9ceb854fea2187bc4d75157fa2dd.poster.avif?t=1747330010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/a81d9ceb854fea2187bc4d75157fa2dd.webm?t=1747330010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3474360/extras/a81d9ceb854fea2187bc4d75157fa2dd.mp4?t=1747330010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
